#

French Blackberry Charlotte

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 70%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

dairygluten

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Tags:

dessertFrench cuisinespecial occasion

Description

A sophisticated French dessert featuring layers of ladyfinger biscuits and a luscious blackberry filling, crowned with a silky whiskey vanilla cream.

Ingredients

  • ladyfingers: 24 pieces
  • blackberries: 500g
  • sugar: 150g
  • lemon juice: 1 tbsp
  • gelatin: 2 sheets
  • heavy cream: 250ml
  • vanilla bean: 1
  • whiskey: 2 tbsp
